import React from 'react'
import UserSideBar from '../../Components/Users/UserSideBar'
export default function UserFavouritProductPage() {
  return (<>
   <Container >
            <Row className='py-3'>
                <Col sm="3" xs="2" md="2">
                    <UserSideBar />
                </Col>

                <Col sm="9" xs="10" md="10">
                    <UserFavoriteProduct />
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>
  </>
    
  )
}
